   @{b}comfortably listing/uncompressing/compressing files and drawers,@{ub}

   (included with the EASys!_Plus package)

   @{" + " SYSTEM "run <>NIL: ${RefTable/Archive-Manager}"} The EASys! Compress-Manager: @{i}${RefTable/Archive-Manager}@{ui}

   compatible to:

       .arj
       .dms
       .lha
       .lzh
       .lzx
       .run
       .tar
       .zip / winzip

       Easy to enhance.


   Since version 3.0 of EASys! the compressmanager supports
   the following @{b}EMail-option@{ub}:

   -sendMail

   The files handed over by arguments will be presented for
   compression or direct sending by mail. Here, such a call
   may be constructed as this example:

   ${RefTable/Archive-Manager} -sendMail ft112@fen.baynet.de sys:utilities

   The same function, but without addressate, is used, when files are
   selected on the workbench and then handed over to the ToolsMenu
   "   - send per mail".


